title: The Perfect Home - Home in Puyallup. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['4 bedroom rambler on peaceful lot with in-ground pool awaits!', 'Don’t miss the opportunity to live close to everything while feeling miles away!', 'Situated on nearly 3/4 acre w/lofty trees, you’ll experience the tranquility the minute you arrive.', 'This home is solidly built, boasts a great layout & is ready for your updates!', 'Spacious kitchen, dining, living rooms, & family room w/fireplace.', "The primary bedroom features ¾ ensuite bath, down the hall you'll find 2 add'l bedrooms & full bath.", 'Another bedroom & ½ bath are on the other side of the living room.', 'Gas furnace & H2O tank.', "You'll love having your own in-ground pool w/concrete patio surround & large entertaining deck!", '2 car garage, storage shed.', 'Close to parks, freeways and amenities!', '***Please Text & Call', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pics***']
